== Highrise Deal Gantt Chart ==

Outputs some PNGs using Google's Graphing API to generate several Gantt charts which display
visually time taken from the start to the finish of deals. Useful when trying to visualise
how long you are spending on deals.

Marshall Jones (marshall@mediapopinc.com)

http://github.com/mjallday/Highrise-Deal-Gantt-Chart

== Documentation ==

None, read the source code and use the following urls to reverse engineer as required.

http://developer.37signals.com/highrise/reference
http://code.google.com/apis/chart/docs/making_charts.html

== Usage ==

python hr.py highrise_api_key https://companyname.highrisehq.com/deals.xml ~/dir_to_output/

